#

Honey Garlic Tofu

25 min
$8
320 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main

Tags:

Quick MealHealthy

Description

A sweet and savory dish that combines crispy tofu with a delicious honey garlic sauce.

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 14 oz
  • honey: 3 tbsp
  • soy sauce: 2 tbsp
  • garlic: 4 cloves
  • vegetable oil: 2 tbsp
  • green onions: 2 stalks
  • sesame seeds: 1 tbsp
